{"id":"mb3geo-new-546","subject":"math","level":"MB3","gradeRange":"Grades 6-8","topic":"Ratios – Advanced","question":"A school's student-to-teacher ratio is 18:1. With 540 students, how many teachers?","options":["30","18","40","54"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"540/18 = 30 teachers."},
